{
  "stem": "6900.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- my brother flew him out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother sent him to a private school where his son was going, and he was with them for about three months.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then my sister-in-law said-- she's in England-- she couldn't look after two boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my cousin-- who was the son of my-- my dad's youngest brother-- took him, and they lived in Kenton in Middlesex, in England.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he sent Maurice to school and then kept him there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are now in Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived-- they lived in South Africa afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now they're in Australia, and we're all-- I'm still in touch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I found out how my daughter died, I think, through my son.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I think that was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] Because the-- the-- the Red Cross letter I had from my brother when I was in the hospital just said that she died in Belsen after the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was with her all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- there was-- I don't know exactly how many children alive, because my son has met them all now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this nurse-- Polish nurse that's just been honored by the Dutch queen and also here, I believe-- looked after the-- she heard children crying, and she went to see where they were, and it was these children that were over.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but my-- I-- my son knows the nurse, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name, because he's met her now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typhus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all-- all the children had typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My son also had typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was united with my son when we got our British passports and we went to England the first time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was--  [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's before I went back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
